<section class="bg-white py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">The Smarter Way to Build: One-Time Close vs Two-Time Close</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
        Our preferred one-time close construction loan offers major advantages over the traditional two-loan process.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-center items-stretch">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-2 border-[#bf9f5c]">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-[#09143e]">One-Time Close (Our Method)</h3>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-file-circle-check text-4xl text-[#bf9f5c] my-4" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-left text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#bf9f5c] mr-2 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"></i><span><strong>One Closing, One Set of Fees:</strong> Save thousands in closing costs.</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#bf9f5c] mr-2 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"></i><span><strong>Rate Locked Upfront:</strong> Protects you from rate hikes during construction.</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#bf9f5c] mr-2 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"></i><span><strong>Seamless Process:</strong> No re-qualification. Your permanent loan is secured from day one.</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-800">Two-Time Close (Traditional)</h3>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-file-circle-question text-4xl text-gray-500 my-4" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-left text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-times text-red-400 mr-2 mt-1"></i><span><strong>Two Closings, Double Fees:</strong> Pay for both a construction loan and separate permanent loan closing.</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-times text-red-400 mr-2 mt-1"></i><span><strong>Rate Risk:</strong> Final mortgage rate isn’t locked until construction finishes.</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-times text-red-400 mr-2 mt-1"></i><span><strong>Re-Qualification Risk:</strong> Must reapply and be re-approved after the build is complete.</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

